cdata.name: SalPay
cdata.desc:
Salarium is an online platform situated in the Philippines. It works as an intermediary between Companies and Employees by providing users with features to monitor the work schedules and payroll requirements.

SalPay is an Ethereum-based token developed by Salarium platform. It aims to be a business tool to help individuals and organizations to send money in south-east Asia with fewer costs and hassles. SAL can be used by Salarium users to send payments to either freelancer or directly hired employees. SalPay's 3.0 will be an ERC20-based algorithm wallet to hold SalPay and other Ethereum-based tokens.
